high_descs: Turn around and walk to the couch and then turn left when you get to it.
Pick up the pillow on the left.
Turn left and walk to the middle of the couch on your left and face it.
Put the pillow in the middle of the couch where the two cushions meet.
Turn left and walk to the pillow.
Pick up the pillow.
Go back to where you put the first pillow.
Put this pillow standing up on end at the bottom of the pillow already there and to it's right.
anns.task_desc: Put two pillows on the couch.

high_descs: Turn around and head to the right to face the blue chair.
Pick up the pillow to the left.
Turn around and face the middle of the tan sofa.
Place the pillow in the middle of the tan sofa.
Move to the left and face the blue chair. pick up the other pillow from the blue chair.
Pick up the other pillow from the blue chair.
Move to the right to face the tan sofa.
Place the pillow next to the other pillow.
anns.task_desc: Move both pillows from the blue chair to the tan sofa.

high_descs: turn around, then turn left to face the grey chair
pick up a cushion on the left
turn right, then look straight at the white, long couch
place the cushion on the couch to the left of the remote
return to the grey chair
pick up the last cushion on the chair
return to the long white couch
place the second cushion so that it is standing up vertically and to the right of the first cushion
